snippet.textDisplay: This wonderful piece of music ,portrays the dark side of an armed conflict which has only produced more martyrs in the course of time. It can be an effective tool to introspect upon the recourse of violence by states in the 21st century. It can be an indication that war as an instrument to solve disputes should be replaced with peaceful means of dispute solving.
